commit.message:
More changes to halls page + more pages!

Also, I added the link to the halls.html file

Updated halls page

- Changed menu to be on top, which made everything 
  below h1 more symmetric and easier to work with
- Deleted the about page because the main page can 
  have information n it( not a lot of info to be said) 
- Added more halls to the page as well as added their 
  pictures to the Pictures folder
- Changed some styles for grouping purposes

Changes to halls.html layout Unspaghetified the code a little bit for styles.css and halls.html. - Added new pictures for the Ellicott community - Got rid of all of the break statements and instead, made paddings for the

tags instead (a lot cleaner)

Added new pictures for Wicomico and Worcester

I fixed two pictures

Changed pictures for Carroll and Caroline hall. *Need better pictures (our own)*

Changed the HTML and CSS to clean up a little bit and change the layout of buttons/pictures on the halls page.
Changed link for Carroll Hall button *need to make separate hall pages*
Added/changed pictures. Added background of UMD logo
Auto stash before merge of "master" and "origin/master"

Did a lot of stuff that I've forgotten about.

Did way more effort than I care to admit
